{"tid":251462,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"因為朋友搞到自己好唔開心","createTime":"2017-05-21T03:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T09:17:04.000Z","uid":78777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0cd4273320607d69aed3ff567acb419d670df79","tid":251462,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:06:04.000Z","msg":"中學做朋友嘅時候係做到老死咁、兄弟咁<br />\n日日一齊食飯、上堂、吹水咁<br />\n依家升到上嚟大專，佢就識到一班friend<br />\n之後就唔再搵我<br />\n相對地佢日日都要係facebook tag佢班新朋友，好似驚人地唔知佢有一班新朋友咁<br />\n而我明明好努力咁嘗試去維繫返個友誼<br />\n(係咁主動whatsapp佢，約佢出街之類)<br />\n但係就feel到佢好似當我陌生人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後就係因為咁搞到個人好唔開心，甚至去睇完社工同醫生之後話我有抑鬱症嘅傾向，叫我咩要睇開啲咁，我同佢講佢就講一句「take care」算<br />\n我發覺自己仲賤過地底泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5de758034c4793c703074cb411c74f49191666b","tid":251462,"uid":36786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:07:38.000Z","msg":"係咪你自己做過啲咩產生左誤會而又唔記得"},{"pid":"ae204219b946d7590c51f587eaa5ca6b0935a96a","tid":251462,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:10:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪你自己做過啲咩產生左誤會而又唔記得</blockquote><br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我記得去12月為止都叫做有日日whatsapp，係去到1月開始佢有識到一班新嘅project mate開始就突然間唔想理我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b990ef4e991433949c2405731f6a80edbf1370f","tid":251462,"uid":71852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:10:57.000Z","msg":"你大專都可以識其他朋友<br />\n無謂留戀以前"},{"pid":"586981314aedc1e18e880bf479088685ab56d454","tid":251462,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:11:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8ec81792c751cc1be59ecee6bd4d8c4b670467f","tid":251462,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:12:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你得一個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己好毒同內向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基本上交到心嘅得一個，依家連個一個都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167e4f35c7584a08025d4d156685ab67e74dde1f","tid":251462,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:15:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"204b818ccd10a0e1df67b6336a62150ab2727033","tid":251462,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:18:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你得一個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己好毒同內向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基本上交到心嘅得一個，依家連個一個都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你朋友係咪好外向</blockquote><br />\n中學時期叫做正常人，即係有好幾個friend嘅<br />\n上到大專頭一個sem都係冇咩朋友，仲同我講咩好似得佢一個重視中同好似好on9咁<br />\n但係Sem 2開始唔知係上莊定點突然間好外向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咁tag人又成"},{"pid":"a7a6f42db59a3765c78308bf8b2570ea220c1718","tid":251462,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:21:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24a1401cee30bed4ee79bdab1e82ea7a8d4469a8","tid":251462,"uid":62737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:57:13.000Z","msg":"我做你朋友啦樓豬"},{"pid":"ac47d1c364f3b5b56b7977da3727663a1dbee280","tid":251462,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:49:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3db66ecc97cd71518d2aa9564f9238e03e6af1bb","tid":251462,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"我前排都好似你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地已經有左新圈子 你已經冇乜價值所以先唔想再你講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你點挽回都冇用㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如試吓響大專識多啲人， join多啲soc活動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再唔係嘅咪上連登tg post識朋友囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825d858cdef6c3291a66ed4163d21b2cf83b86f9","tid":251462,"uid":106037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:59:00.000Z","msg":"到佢哋有嘢要人幫嘅時候就會知中同嘅重要性 <br />\n雖然咁講好現實 但呢個世界真係咁運作 人永遠都係貪新鮮嘅 不過我覺得無論大學點熟點好都唔及中同<br />\n樓主都唔好太過執著 試下識吓新朋友喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f600511a0022045d62a8535de674cb2f5602c6a","tid":251462,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4984da877208298b2de0586b99d4145411ef3820","tid":251462,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:29:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a845dd8bf828439b6517aced50bc0ab08c7a7e3a","tid":251462,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29ad8ca7d6195ca1d9f8a1b627d198c237a3ed3c","tid":251462,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我前排都好似你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地已經有左新圈子 你已經冇乜價值所以先唔想再你講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你點挽回都冇用㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如試吓響大專識多啲人， join多啲soc活動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再唔係嘅咪上連登tg post識朋友囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家搞到連識朋友都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好辛苦"}]}